n<br />\n你嘅大志壯闊<br />\n你嘅勇氣無比。<br />\n<br />\n男兒應當放眼天下<br />\n答應我，留有用身，幹一番大事業 ！"},{"pid":"d01d164d46dbb43a4dff65d8e46b25769b458d92","tid":1738812,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"靜靜地"},{"pid":"a5dcdfb0806d8bead59eb45b1ab6858e78337c31","tid":1738812,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:52:41.000Z","msg":"絕望之際嘅 to-do list<br />\n<br />\n1. 留命，唔准自殺自殘，要好手好腳<br />\n2. 每日鍛鍊身體<br />\n(#3擇一或多個進行)<br />\n3a. 準備文宣材料，加入文宣組<br />\n3b. 準備文具加入勇武，身體鍛鍊到咁上吓就開得波<br />\n3c. 留意各個哨兵頻道，有興趣睇水報料可以幫手做哨<br />\n4. 難受嘅時候中止接收抗爭資訊，進行心理層面嘅休息"},{"pid":"75faf8f11987e29ac631feb7056b0ca7bdfcd39d","tid":1738812,"uid":270943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e61d868a0b4927dd033233e387ed09b641bcdd01","tid":1738812,"uid":320807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d6c5650f77772d40c614ada63d489a72b5e1801","tid":1738812,"uid":117437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:41:04.000Z","msg":"巴打， 勇武靠你， 留有用之驅<br />\n雖然周圍都係d 野狗又鬧，但你一定唔會驚，既， 支持你"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:42:28.000Z","msg":"我未發過夢，唔知點入手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"想幫手嘅聽日去黎明行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死咗就見唔到香港贏嘅時候"},{"pid":"4c2e93134c462f3fa2141ef3143e0468040413ac","tid":1738812,"uid":239615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f9e8394d9f204a03b8e2bd931131666c0dbcbe4","tid":1738812,"uid":320807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22732828211a5136284b4f8d3557fe94b9e2d756","tid":1738812,"uid":239615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"你想被自殺合理化？呢個就係你依家做緊嘅野..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"咁比指示我應該做啲乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"咪撚死...